---
title: Tex Mex Shrimp with Veggies and Bowtie Pasta Salad
description: It’s hard not to love farfalle—their tiny bowtie shape is just precious. Tossed with juicy mexican spiced shrimp, corn and crisp peppers this 30-minute pasta is bound to become a part of your weeknight repertoire.
